 万。在一篇点赞超 2.7 万、评论超过 1000 条的视频中，有网友提出疑问：「真的不伤膝盖吗？」「会不会影响到真正游泳的人？」 无锡一家游泳健身馆工作人员告诉记者：「游泳池跑步健身燃脂是有科学依据的，这种锻炼方式不需要教练教学，自己就能自主进行。只要水深达到胸腔位置就会有很好的效果，不仅可以减轻膝盖的磨损，还可以达到有阻力情况下进行全身运动的目的。」 就部分网友担心游泳池跑步影响到正常游泳，该工作人员解释道：「我们的泳池是有规划的，有专门培训泳道和自由游泳道，如果有人上课，就不去培训泳道就好了。而且泳池的水是由浅到深的，浅的地方 1.2 米，深水区 1.8 米，可根据身高量力而行。」游泳池跑步成新健身方式？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-009383b827f8354301f53a88b4f5298c_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "71 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2023795237672286121"}}, "attached_info": "CkoIvpPi2tLTtqUPEAMaCTExOTAyMjA5MiCQkMPOBjAAOKsBQBNyEzIwMjM3OTUyMzc2NzIyODYxMjF4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "20_1777218135.553776", "card_id": "Q_2028043318978691458", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 33}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "有没有一件你坚持了三年的事?"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-5bd28eed5049e09e9f506f417e32fb31.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "69 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2028043318978691458"}}, "attached_info": "CkkIvpPi2tLTtqUPEAMaCTExOTE2MDUyMCDm+IDPBjAAOF9AFHITMjAyODA0MzMxODk3ODY5MTQ1OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "21_1777218135.554020", "card_id": "Q_671133917", "card_label": {"type": "new", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-a4b0b52b561281109c51e4957cb20130_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-10ef6526c602e55a8c606e46aa0cc586_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 47}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "体制内如何快速提高自己的的公文写作水平？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "体制内政研室新人，每天面对各种要写的材料不知所措，如何才能快速提高自己的公文写作水平？"}, "image_area": {